The '''Native Management and Industrialization Service''' or '''NAMIS''' was a project run by the [[Coalition for Progress/Legends|Coalition for Progress]] that sought to bring economic prosperity to worlds. It failed disastrously on [[Gamorr/Legends|Gamorr]].

